<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Richmond</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Established in 1950, the community in Richmond is renowned for its eclectic mix of housing units that range from the post-war age bungalows to the modern apartment condominiums and infills. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Since a number of properties date back several decades, there has been massive reconstruction projects to renovate the bungalows in order to align them with the needs and expectations of the contemporary homebuyer. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Homes for sale in Richmond are readily available between a price range of $300,000 up to around a million as well. </p>
        </div>
